content:
[Lucent](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/lucent-clipboard-history/id6757361230?mt=12) 是一款功能更加强大的剪切板app, 在基础的剪切板历史功能上增加了许多便捷工具.

针对图片数据: 
- 支持一键转换格式;
- 调用tinypng进行压缩;
- 上传到imgbb图床;
- 根据分辨率匹配Apple设备进行截图套壳美化;
<img width="300" height="513" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a32b28ea-1cd7-4556-b86c-7699ab708b86" />

<img width="300" height="2660" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/24c7dd98-08b5-43c6-83c0-c73254cb47bf" />

视频:
- 一键转换格式/ 压缩;
- 制作GIF;
<img width="300" height="610" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/627c1961-f16e-4c1f-b75f-6994ef601fad" />

<img width="180" height="714" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bcf24c3c-1db8-44c5-9f2d-05e3451f83c0" />

由于App Store审核原因, 自动粘贴功能需要下载一个额外的[工具](https://lucentapp.cc/integration);
